Perl-module to ease the interaction with my database.

WARNING: May be of very limited use for others! The main reason for putting it 
online was that an other project depends on this module.

If you still want to use it: 
Read the pod inside of the code and the comments in DBToolsCfg-TEMPLATE.pm

